# Cybersecurity Awareness Chatbot

##  Description
This is a C# console chatbot designed to educate users about basic cybersecurity concepts such as passwords, phishing, safe browsing, malware, VPNs, and 2FA.

## Features
- ASCII hacker-style banner
- Voice greeting using WAV file
- Interactive chatbot
- Keyword recognition system
- Typing animation effect
- Input validation

## Technologies Used
- C#
- .NET Console Application
- System.Media (for audio)

## How to Run
1. Open the project in Visual Studio
2. Run the program
3. Enter your name
4. Ask questions about cybersecurity (e.g. phishing, password, malware)
5. Type 'exit' to quit

